: 456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brits defeatedJapan's Kei Nishikori and Taro Daniel and return to action against Belgium's Sander Gille and Joran Vliegen in the second round tonight.\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 459, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Brits\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\"}, {\"begin\": 485, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kei Nishikori\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\"}, {\"begin\": 503, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taro Daniel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taro_Daniel\"}, {\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9928142308407837, \"rank\": 0.004960942627703097, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_Davis_Cup_team\"}, {\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joran_Vliegen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joran Vliegen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joran_Vliegen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joran_Vliegen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"the second round\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of their next battle on the clay courts in Paris, it has come to light the big sacrifice Evans made in order to compete at the Olympics with Murray.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 664, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999794151793, \"rank\": 2.0584803273373245e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 762, \"end\": 768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2950030520039087e-34, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their next battle\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"the clay courts\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"the big sacrifice\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"Evans\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Evans took a big rankings drop in order to feature at the Games - a decision which has seen him brutally drop all the way down from world No.58 to No.169.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Evans\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"a big rankings\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"world No.58\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"No.169\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's because Evans had significant ranking points to defend at the ATP 500 Washington Open, where he landed the second Tour title of his career last year.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9995578482900574, \"rank\": 0.0004423472942696318, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"significant ranking points\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"the ATP 500 Washington Open\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"the second Tour title\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dan Evans dropped 111 spots in the ATP rankings to #169He was #58 & had Washington to defend, but he chose to play the OlympicsThe Olympics are special for everyone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 but I have a feeling the chance to play doubles with Andy Murray 1 last time played a big factor in his\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6pic.twitter.com/ZELLY7Cxv7 Evans will not mind, though, after making an Olympic memory he will never forget next to a true icon of British sport,who is set to retire as soon as the event ends.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1085, \"end\": 1094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.8112039312538128, \"rank\": 0.2327356432433034, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 1120, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_Tennis_Professionals\", \"score\": 0.9999999048495783, \"rank\": 9.515046499951482e-08, \"text\": \"ATP rankings\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_Tennis_Professionals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_of_Tennis_Professionals\"}, {\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Huskies_football\", \"score\": 0.999114738222443, \"rank\": 0.0006531351661461955, \"text\": \"Washington\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Huskies_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Huskies_football\"}, {\"begin\": 1491, \"end\": 1498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9999992993966952, \"rank\": 6.932059318579523e-07, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"111 spots\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"the OlympicsThe Olympics\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"a feeling\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"doubles\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"Andy Murray\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"a big factor\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"his\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6pic.twitter.com/ZELLY7Cxv7\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"Evans\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic memory\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"a true icon\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have never saved five match points in a row and I never will again - he certainly will not,' Evans said.\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1650, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9995578482900574, \"rank\": 0.0004423472942696318, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five match points\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's something I will remember forever but it would be amazing if we could go on to do something really special this week.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knows it's his last tournament so sometimes he might think about that but he did a great job of getting us up and the crowd involved.'\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his last tournament\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"a great job\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dan Evans on fending off five match points\\u2026 'It's amazing,' Evans said.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1926, \"end\": 1935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.8112039312538128, \"rank\": 0.2327356432433034, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 1992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9995578482900574, \"rank\": 0.0004423472942696318, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five match points\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I guess at 4-9 [in the tie-break] I just did not want to miss the shot to end his career!\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tie-break\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"the shot\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It sums him up.\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's amazing.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Honestly, the best feeling for me to be a part of that.'\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Honestly, the best feeling\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray, meanwhile, added: 'In terms of my great comebacks, it's probably up there.\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2178, \"end\": 2184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2950030520039087e-34, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2213}, {\"ngram\": \"my great comebacks\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not think [I have saved five match points] in a row - in singles it's almost impossible to do that, so I do not think I have ever done that before.\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five match points\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Certainly from my side, I did not think I was playing well and both of us can play much better than that.\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my side\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In my career I have turned around a lot of matches I have looked unlikely to win, I have had that mental toughness, strength that was, at times, questioned early in my career.\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2565}, {\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2576}, {\"ngram\": \"that mental toughness\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2640}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am really proud of that - I always try my best to fight and figure out ways to come though.\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2797, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'When it mattered, I raised my level - and I need to try and find a way of starting the match like that in a couple of days' time.\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my level\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2835}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2870}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2892}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"days' time\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it clicks for us, we have the potential to play really well together because our games complement each other really well.'\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 3057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2974}, {\"ngram\": \"our games\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3021}]}, {\"se